      "text": "Five..."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8640.0,
      "end_time": 11080.0,
      "text": "Five steps to learning a new language."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11360.0,
      "end_time": 11860.0,
      "text": "#1"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 11860.0,
      "end_time": 15760.0,
      "text": "If your language has a new writing system, you have to start with the alphabet."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 16360.0,
      "end_time": 17860.0,
      "text": "Why?, well..."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 17860.0,
      "end_time": 20160.0,
      "text": "If you're learning a language like Japanese or Chinese..."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 21460.0,
      "end_time": 24900.0,
      "text": "and you rely on the Romaji and the Pinyin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 25000.0,
      "end_time": 29000.0,
      "text": "you are going to run into a lot of problems later down the line."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 29000.0,
      "end_time": 31540.0,
      "text": "Obviously this depends on your goals for the language."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 31600.0,
      "end_time": 34240.0,
      "text": "You just want to be conversational and never be able to read?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 34240.0,
      "end_time": 36440.0,
      "text": "Go ahead, don't learn the script."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 36440.0,
      "end_time": 40520.0,
      "text": "But my suggestion is to first start learning the script of language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 40960.0,
      "end_time": 45540.0,
      "text": "because... you'll be able to pronounce things a lot easier because you're not relying on an"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45760.0,
      "end_time": 47620.0,
      "text": "English rendering of the language."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 47780.0,
      "end_time": 48500.0,
      "text": "Tip #2"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 48500.0,
      "end_time": 53980.0,
      "text": "After I finish learning the alphabet I move into basic greetings and vocabulary."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 54320.0,
      "end_time": 55520.0,
      "text": "This sound obvious but..."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 55520.0,
      "end_time": 58440.0,
      "text": "it's so easy to learn this in any language."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 58440.0,
      "end_time": 61880.0,
      "text": "And as soon as you're over that little hurdle you'll feel really good about yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 61940.0,
      "end_time": 63660.0,
      "text": "and you can start talking to people."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 63660.0,
      "end_time": 67940.0,
      "text": "I also suggest you learn the 100 most used words in the language."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 68300.0,
      "end_time": 69720.0,
      "text": "You're gonna hear these words a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 69720.0,
      "end_time": 73060.0,
      "text": "they're gonna pop up in movies, on the radio, in music, in books."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 73520.0,
      "end_time": 77000.0,
      "text": "So if you know the basic greetings and vocabulary and a bit of grammar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 77100.0,
      "end_time": 80440.0,
      "text": "as well as a hundred most useful or must common words..."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80640.0,
      "end_time": 82360.0,
      "text": "You're already at a very good place."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82540.0,
      "end_time": 83300.0,
      "text": "Step #3"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 83300.0,
      "end_time": 85420.0,
      "text": "That brings me to grammar, my"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 85520.0,
      "end_time": 86180.0,
      "text": "favorite."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 86320.0,
      "end_time": 87640.0,
      "text": "I'm so in love with grammar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 87700.0,
      "end_time": 91900.0,
      "text": "I think I learn more... grammar structures than I do vocabulary."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 92040.0,
      "end_time": 93360.0,
      "text": "Learning grammar structure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 93360.0,
      "end_time": 95360.0,
      "text": "write it down hundreds of times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 95360.0,
      "end_time": 97360.0,
      "text": "and pop in new vocabulary words."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 97420.0,
      "end_time": 99940.0,
      "text": "That way you'll learn how to use the structure..."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 100460.0,
      "end_time": 102460.0,
      "text": "and you're learning new words at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 103000.0,
      "end_time": 103500.0,
      "text": "#4"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 103500.0,
      "end_time": 104440.0,
      "text": "Practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 104660.0,
      "end_time": 106660.0,
      "text": "You need to get a language partner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 106740.0,
      "end_time": 109820.0,
      "text": "and you need to make sure you're using the language every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 109820.0,
      "end_time": 111820.0,
      "text": "If you don't use this language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 112520.0,
      "end_time": 113760.0,
      "text": "at least for a week..."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 113920.0,
      "end_time": 116200.0,
      "text": "I mean if you learn for a while and you stop for a week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 116200.0,
      "end_time": 118040.0,
      "text": "you're gonna forget so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 118360.0,
      "end_time": 122440.0,
      "text": "So even if you have to force yourself just to do a five or ten minutes a day, do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 122440.0,
      "end_time": 125680.0,
      "text": "because it will stimulate your short and long-term memory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 125680.0,
      "end_time": 127640.0,
      "text": "And you'll remember things a lot better."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 127960.0,
      "end_time": 130460.0,
      "text": "So put in that effort to do a little bit each day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 130560.0,
      "end_time": 132520.0,
      "text": "and you will not disappoint yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 132780.0,
      "end_time": 133280.0,
      "text": "Aaand..."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 133280.0,
      "end_time": 135400.0,
      "text": "I bet you guys can guess what number five is..."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 135400.0,
