      "text": "Keep track of your progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 137400.0,
      "end_time": 142440.0,
      "text": "Not even gonna go into detail because I think I've spoken about this so many times."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 142580.0,
      "end_time": 146340.0,
      "text": "Surround yourself with the culture, with books, with music."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 146840.0,
